data.title: 准备以至少20秒的时间回答以下问题
data.answer: I would like a see a natural phenomenon in Denmark, called "black sun". During March and April, in the southwestern marshlands of Denmark, you can experience the “sort sol”, which literally means black sun. Sort sol is the event when up to one million birds flock to the sky during sunset and the sun is actually blocked by the birds, hence the name "black sun".（68 字）
data.referenceText: Describe a natural phenomenon that you would like to see or experience, and explain why.
data.referenceTranslate: 描述一个你想看到或经历的自然现象，并解释原因。
